high_descs: Turn right, go to the wall, turn right, go to the toilet.
Pick up the blue bottle of lotion from the back of the toilet that is closest to you.
Turn around and go to the counter.
Put the lotion on the counter just to the left of the rightmost sink.
Turn right, go to the wall, turn right, go to the toilet.
Pick up the blue bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and go to the counter.
Put the bottle of lotion on the counter just to the right of the leftmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of lotion on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the closest soap bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the counter.
Put the soap bottle on the counter in between the two sinks.
Walk back over to the toilet.
Pick up the soap bottle off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the soap bottle on the counter in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Move two soap bottles to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the toilet
Pick up the nearest blue pump bottle from the toilet
Turn around and walk up to the counter between the sinks
Put the bottle on the counter
Turn around and walk back to the toilet
Pick up the pump bottle from the toilet
Turn around and walk back to the counter
Put the pump bottle on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the pump bottles on the bathroom counter
